{"tid":393232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挑起港獨、劉曉波爭議 蔡若蓮兒子之死或成第一滴血","createTime":"2017-09-09T05:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T06:05:19.000Z","uid":35370,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cca0da379edf4abcc16216b21ed3c5daee23422","tid":393232,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日有班人唔肯踏出嚟，話要有第一滴血先至會改變<br />\n<br />\n睇怕蔡若蓮個仔就係傳說中呢一滴血啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9885b2eca1f6851eb8462db9d0f41f18229dbd50","tid":393232,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"教大真係幫倒忙<br />\n死個仔已經慘，係人傷口灑鹽，全世界都知佢比人笑<br />\n仲要驚動到特首回應，成個世界都知佢死個仔比人笑<br />\n為咗上位R funding真係無所不用其極"},{"pid":"1643895c4e65a64b90d65898025434066ca2ee05","tid":393232,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T05:56:20.000Z","msg":"好勝老母誓不言敗<br />\n個仔生時，就消費個仔頻頻登報講育兒<br />\n死咗個仔都係輸唔落呢啖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔准笑！實捉到你！！<br />\n<br />\n得啦，特首都幫你出啖氣啦<br />\n好勝老母應該覺得自己贏曬啲網民，心涼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/28179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F28179.jpg&h=42946931&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b0b1f10907ce11546e29ad698186b626e18f42a","tid":393232,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:03:36.000Z","msg":"問心講句，本身死個仔過幾日都冇人講<br />\n現實上有人奚落嘅時候，或者有口德村居民叫收口<br />\n<br />\n但教大校長鍾意熱鬧辦喪，唔比死者安息，挑起仇恨<br />\n本來會同情你嘅人，都變成一齊笑鳩你<br />\n冇人可憐你，愈來愈憎你<br />\n依家仲燒埋去劉曉波度，中共都比你丟架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>乜依家搞教育嘅人可以冇智商架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8470a26f3163956725595d69592a7204b19e7e46","tid":393232,"uid":35370,"like":